/**
 * CustomStyles.astro
 *
 * This component imports and manages custom font assets for the site.
 * It serves as a centralized location for font loading and CSS variable definitions.
 * Currently configured to use the Inter variable font, with commented alternatives available.
 *
 * Features:
 * - Font loading via @fontsource-variable for optimized performance
 * - Support for variable fonts with multiple weight ranges
 * - Centralized font management for consistent typography
 * - Commented alternative font options for easy switching
 *
 * Font Integration:
 * - @fontsource-variable/inter: Primary font loading for Inter variable font
 * - Alternative fonts listed as comments for quick substitution
 *
 * Data Flow:
 * 1. Imports specified font packages
 * 2. Makes fonts available through CSS custom properties
 * 3. Provides fallback options through commented imports
 *
 * Usage Context:
 * - Included in BaseLayout for site-wide font availability
 * - Renders in document head for early font loading
 * - Supports both variable and static font implementations
 *
 * Available Font Options (commented):
 * - DM Sans
 * - Nunito
 * - Dosis
 * - Outfit
 * - Roboto
 * - Literata
 * - IBM Plex Sans
 * - Karla
 * - Poppins
 * - Fira Sans
 * - Libre Franklin
 * - Inconsolata
 * - Raleway
 * - Oswald
 * - Space Grotesk
 * - Urbanist
 *
 * Implementation Notes:
 * - Variable fonts provide better performance through single file loading
 * - Font weights and styles are interpolated rather than discrete files
 * - Alternative fonts can be activated by uncommenting import statements
 * - CSS custom properties should be defined in theme files for font usage
 */

import '@fontsource-variable/inter';

